original_title: Stephen K Amos - The Feel Good Factor
overview: Stephen K Amos is guaranteed to provide you with the feel good factor in this laugh a minute stand-up performance filmed in front of a sell-out audience at the Hammersmith Apollo. Star of Montreal, Melbourne and Edinburgh festivals, Amos is a hit with critics and audiences alike and has a swagger of awards in tow. In fact he's so flipping good he's only gone and got his very own BBC show called, you guessed it The Stephen K Amos Show.
title: Stephen K Amos - The Feel Good Factor
